    rdfs:label "ECRR Base metadata" ;
    dct:abstract "Schema defining mandatory properties for all EarthCube Resource Registry (ECRR) resource types. Includes resource identity, type classification via mainEntity, and licensing. Defines properties: @id, @type, schema:name, schema:description, schema:mainEntity, schema:license. Uses building blocks: labeledLink (schemaorgProperties)."^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
